# Flutter conventions

## Layout

```
lib/
  app/           # MaterialApp, router, theme
  l10n/          # ARB + generated localizations
  core/          # shared utils, constants
  features/<name>/
    data/
    domain/
    presentation/  # bloc, screen, widgets
  shared/widgets/
```

## Bloc

- One `Bloc` or `Cubit` per feature flow; `equatable` for states/events
- Provide blocs at shell via `MultiBlocProvider`
- UI: `BlocBuilder` / `BlocListener`; no business logic in widgets

## UI

- Material 3 only (`useMaterial3: true`)
- Colors from `Theme.of(context).colorScheme`
- Use generated `AppLocalizations` — no hardcoded user-facing strings

## Platforms

- Android + iOS only — do not add web/desktop targets
